<p class="">In reply to the first supplementary question, the immediate cost to the Treasury is estimated at £360,000 a year, and it will increase to £600,000 a year gradually, until, probably about 20 or 25 years' time; thereafter it will decrease, as the number of officers is adjusted to the required establishment.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
